e B\u00e2le le 6 mai 1936, les fonctionnaires allemands responsables ne pouvant \u00eatre poursuivis. Wesemann fut expuls\u00e9 apr\u00e8s sa lib\u00e9ration, en 1938. Enlev\u00e9 une seconde fois par la Gestapo \u00e0 Lisbonne en 1941, Jacob mourut \u00e0 Berlin en 1944 des suites de sa d\u00e9tention."]], "text_links": [[], [{"start": 3, "end": 9, "mention": null, "origin": "entity_fishing", "annotation": {"wikidata_entity_id": "Q2401", "wikipedia_page_id": 3716, "wikipedia_page_title": null, "wikidata_entity_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q2401", "grobid_tag": null, "extra_fields": {"rawName": "Berlin", "confidence_score": 0.8312, "domains": ["Architecture"], "origin": "entity_fishing"}}}, {"start": 18, "end": 22, "mention": null, "origin": "entity_fishing", "annotation": {"wikidata_entity_id": "Q78", "wikipedia_page_id": 12274, "wikipedia_page_title": null, "wikidata_entity_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q78", "grobid_tag": null, "extra_fields": {"rawName": "Berlin", "confidence_score": 0.8312, "domains": ["Architecture"], "origin": "entity_fishing"}}, "href": "fr/articles/007478", "dhsid": "007478", "wiki": {"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q78", "itemLabel": "B\u00e2le", "dhsid": "007478", "namefr": "B\u00e2le", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%C3%A2le", "namede": "Basel", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Basel", "nameit": "Basilea", "articleit": "https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Basilea", "nameen": "Basel", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Basel", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q14770218", "instanceofLabel": "capitale cantonale de Suisse", "gndid": "4004617-5", "wikidata_id": "Q78"}}, {"start": 27, "end": 41, "mention": null, "origin": "entity_fishing", "annotation": {"wikidata_entity_id": "Q214183", "wikipedia_page_id": 3659357, "wikipedia_page_title": null, "wikidata_entity_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q214183", "grobid_tag": null, "extra_fields": {"rawName": "Berlin", "confidence_